creator: FinMeUp
descriptionHtml:
Follow industry experts as they share the latest insights in finance from crypto, entrepreneurial advice and their top stock picks. Get access to curated financial content that saves you the time of researching countless articles. All are available in a simple news feed that gets you closer to financial freedom.

CLEARING YOUR PATH TO FINANCIAL INDEPENDENCE
FinMeUp is your financial platform - providing you with all the financial and investment-related information you need across several categories (crypto, stocks, tax, credit, property, startups, business, economics and more).

LEARN FROM THE BEST
Trusted and verified mentors are sharing their market analysis, investing strategies, stock picks, and more so that you don’t have to spend the time finding the most relevant content.

OVER 20+ PROFESSIONAL AND VETTED MENTORS
All FinMeUp Mentors go through a verification process to ensure you receive top-quality content from the best.

FinMeUp FEATURES
1. NEWS FEED - view, filter or search your personalised content from the Mentors you trust, or view them all, the choice is yours.
2. EXPLORE - find the content you are looking for from the Mentors you like by using the Explore section. Search within specific categories to find the content you need.

SUBSCRIPTION TERMS
If you subscribe via Apple, payment will be charged to App Store Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the rate of the selected plan. Subscriptions and auto-renewal may be managed by going to Account Settings after purchase.

DISCLAIMER
FinMeUp is a platform for financial education and information. Nothing on the FinMeUp app should be viewed as financial advice. All content on the platform is only an opinion of the author(s). All content is purely subjective and you should do your own due diligence.

See our Privacy Policy at https://finmeup.co.za/privacypolicy
See our Terms & Conditions at https://finmeup.co.za/termsandconditions
